SUNDAY SUN and Kaizer Chiefs are giving away double tickets to Amakhosi&rsquo;s Absa Premiership match against Bloemfontein Celtic at FNB Stadium on Wednesday, 14 December. To win your set of tickets, SMS the keyword &ldquo;AMAKHOSI&rdquo; to 34580 (R1,50), followed by your name, surname and residential address. Please note that winners will be expected to collect their tickets at the Daily Sun offices at Media Park, 69 Kingsway Avenue, Auckland Park.